comment:
I have followed this case for some time now and have seen the court documents and the evidence presented. There is  no doubt in my mind at all that Amber Heard is not only the abuser in this case, but a blatant liar and shameless manipulator.
But no-one should take anyones word for that. Go and review the evidence and the facts of the case available and make up your own mind. 
It's so vitally important in this time of hearsay and media bias and dishonesty, to be able to access facts and evidence so you can determine their credibility for yourself.
The channels that I follow and  know to be covering this case in depth, going over evidence and court documents, are the following: 

Lost Beyond Pluto    (she is a lawyer and goes through the court documents and the case from a law perspective -very informative)
ThatUmbrellaGuy    (Great content, always directly backed by the latest evidence)
Stevie J Raw     (also absolutely excellent at going through the evidence and facts - has full readings of witness and defence statements)
Come Geek Some    (same, references and goes over facts and court documents)
Colonel Kurtz     (has very interesting in-depth content on the case from a more psychological/philosophical angle)

As mentioned, Stevie J Raw has uploaded FULL unedited readings of the court statements of Amber Heard, Johnny Depp and other important key persons in the case, giving you direct access to their own statements so you can compare and come up with your own opinion as to who is telling the truth.

comment: I was trafficked by my mother. Born in a hospital raised in a hotel. I've only just started speaking about it, since I was told the whole story when I met my mother in my late teens early twenties, where she justified her actions saying she needed money and I was getting in the way of her work because I was crying while she was beining men back. It turned most of them off, most. So no she didn't allow penetrarion, mom of the year,  but I was still passed around like a basketball in a scummy motel until she found someone to live with who got me out of there. I had scabies, bruises, head to toe and was malnourished at 4 months old. When I met her, she tried to get me to work the corner with her for drugmoney, I had no idea what I had gotten myself into, I was alone and I thought I had found my mom, someone who would unconditionally love me, not like the adopted parents who divorced and discarded me.  But she wasn't what I had hoped, and she only confirmed what I had been told my whole life, she was trash. Unfortunately my adopted mother was abusive, and neglectful to where I was molested again as a small child, when I went to get cans to recycle from a neighbor.  I know they say hurt people hurt, but I would never wish what happened to me on anyone. Of anything its made me want to share my story. And the cycle of abuse I grew so comfortable with, I tried to make the man who raped and took my virginity my boyfriend to justify what hadhappened. He didn't want me. I feel gross typing this all out. I just am so digusted anyone would lie.....I've never named my abusers and how could I...when one is my mother. Amber, you're an awful person and if me sharing what has happened to me will help other people come forward who may feel scared too because of her. I'm scared too, but we have to be brave for ourselves, and support eachother. We can't band wagon cancel people, look how much harm its caused poor Johnny.
